item.description: Projects Below are a few projects I have created for my computational biology course. These demonstrate my skills in R and RStudio for data science: Exploratory Data Analysis with Tidyverse Tools (Computational Biology Project) Modeling, Testing, and Classification (Computational Biology Project) Roger Springs Archaeological Site Analysis (Biostatistics Project using the data from my honor’s thesis project)
